151
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:36,490
Kaswal na komento lang iyon.

152
00:12:37,100 --> 00:12:38,370
Bakit ang seryoso mo?

153
00:12:40,130 --> 00:12:41,460
Tiyak na pinagkakatiwalaan kita.

154
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:44,180
Pero may tiwala ka ba sa akin?

155
00:12:47,460 --> 00:12:48,530
Pumunta ako dito pagkatanggap ng

156
00:12:48,530 --> 00:12:49,420
Mensahe ni Jiang Ai.

157
00:12:50,060 --> 00:12:51,060
Ngayon, kami ay nangangailangan

158
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:51,900
ng may kakayahang mga kamay.

159
00:12:52,890 --> 00:12:54,730
Kung kayo ni Jiang Ai ay naghihinala sa isa't isa,

160
00:12:54,980 --> 00:12:56,490
maghihinala rin ang ibang mga panginoon.

161
00:12:58,980 --> 00:12:59,820
Yan.

162
00:13:05,460 --> 00:13:06,370
ayoko

163
00:13:06,370 --> 00:13:07,250
isa pang trahedya.

164
00:13:16,650 --> 00:13:17,490
Sorry, Simu.

165
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:19,610
Masyado akong walang iniisip.

166
00:13:25,180 --> 00:13:26,020
Bilang Kanang Kamay,

167
00:13:27,300 --> 00:13:28,850
ginagawa mo ang lahat para sa kaligtasan ng Void.

168
00:13:35,130 --> 00:13:36,300
At kaibigan mo rin ako.

169
00:13:38,010 --> 00:13:38,980
Sa tabi ng aking trono,

170
00:13:40,490 --> 00:13:42,010
