171
00:13:46,610 --> 00:13:47,450
Huwag kang mag-alala.

172
00:13:48,490 --> 00:13:49,420
Pangako ko

173
00:13:49,420 --> 00:13:50,650
upang alisin ang lahat ng mga hadlang para sa iyo.

174
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:04,220
Pare, umuubo ka na naman.

175
00:14:08,940 --> 00:14:09,940
Ako lang

176
00:14:10,130 --> 00:14:10,970
sa mahinang kalusugan.

177
00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:12,020
Relapse lang yan.

178
00:14:12,770 --> 00:14:13,610
Umupo ka na.

179
00:14:15,220 --> 00:14:16,060
Muntik na akong gumaling

180
00:14:16,060 --> 00:14:16,900
mula sa aking mga sugat.

181
00:14:17,940 --> 00:14:18,820
kaya kong tumayo.

182
00:14:20,700 --> 00:14:22,770
Anong mga plano mo para sa hinaharap?

183
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:25,460
Malupit ang larangan ng digmaan.

184
00:14:26,340 --> 00:14:27,220
Noong nandoon ka,

185
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:28,370
nasaktan ka ng husto.

186
00:14:28,890 --> 00:14:29,730
Huwag ka nang bumalik doon.

187
00:14:30,980 --> 00:14:32,130
Ngayon ka lang may sinecure.

188
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,580
Pero sinusuportahan ka namin ni Chancellor Du.

189
00:14:36,250 --> 00:14:37,980
Maaaring makuha ka ng iyong karanasan sa hukbo

190
00:14:37,980 --> 00:14:39,460
