441
00:30:16,770 --> 00:30:17,730
Kung tatanungin mo ako niyan,

442
00:30:18,090 --> 00:30:19,980
Naalala kong medyo mahina ang boses niya

443
00:30:20,860 --> 00:30:22,290
nung kinausap niya ako.

444
00:30:24,290 --> 00:30:27,010
Sa mga araw na ito, siya ay nangangaso ng mga puppet.

445
00:30:28,290 --> 00:30:29,330
Pwede bang...?

446
00:30:29,490 --> 00:30:30,810
Sinasabi mo bang

447
00:30:31,460 --> 00:30:32,900
Baka nasugatan ang kanyang Grace?

448
00:30:35,250 --> 00:30:36,290
Nakipag-away ba siya

449
00:30:36,290 --> 00:30:37,220
